    • prepareMetadataElement

      public static RsMetaDataElement prepareMetadataElement​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String type) throws SyntaxException, java.lang.IllegalArgumentException

      Prepare metadata element by it's name and type. Metadata element type BNF is:

      <type> ::= <type_name>['('<length>['.'<fractional>]')'][' as ' {<alias>|'"'<alias>'"'}
      • <type_name> - valid SQL name (VARCHAR,INTEGER etc)
      • <length> - field length, if applicable for the given type
      • <fractional> - field precision, if applicable for the given type
      • <alias> - any alias name. If missing, equals to field name
      Parameters:
      name - field name
      type - field type (see syntax above)
      Returns:
      metadata element. Can't be null
      Throws:
      java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if any parameter is null or empty
      SyntaxException - on any syntax errors in the type string
